# Resources directory for zero-trust-architecture-designer

This directory contains:
- policy-library/ - ABAC policy templates (JSON)
- architecture-diagrams/ - ZTA reference architectures (PNG/SVG)
- compliance-mapping.csv - Control mappings (NIST 800-53, CMMC, PCI-DSS)
- ztmm-assessment-template.xlsx - CISA ZTMM pillar assessment worksheet
- metrics-dashboard.json - Grafana/Datadog dashboard spec for ZTA metrics
